pullRequest.title: Composite jmx attributes fix
pullRequest.bodyText:
Fixes #304
Changes

broken open beans fixed "Acceptor/AcceptorAddresses", "Acceptor/Sessions", "Initiator/Sessions" by #205

commit.message: use item name as description when description not provided

nodes.bodyText: This is the base fix caused by #205. Use name as description otherwise an exception will be thrown.
